## What is ATS?
ATS = Applicant Tracking System
It is software that scans resumes before
a human recruiter ever sees them.
If your resume does not match the job
description keywords — it gets rejected
automatically! Most companies use ATS.

## Job Description Targeted
- Role: Data Analyst (Fresher)
